{"tid":916942,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[開箱] 打機神器 - Logitech G keyboard & mouse","createTime":"2018-11-26T04:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T18:22:33.000Z","uid":171743,"like":8,"dislike":81,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d99d81991fb59eab98d33a5a58eb73e701f69185","tid":916942,"uid":171743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:58:30.000Z","msg":"終於搵到機會換晒成 set keyboard &amp; mouse啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落黃金行左轉, 決定入手G pro ~$2000<br />\n(畀左好大勇氣買滑鼠)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/12/oLFc7s.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2FoLFc7s.jpeg&h=3e805d12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/12/9h0n3X.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2F9h0n3X.jpeg&h=9b22294d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/10/GcDSw2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2FGcDSw2.jpeg&h=40114538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/10/pKAeLF.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2FpKAeLF.jpeg&h=02572e8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/10/kMpfAU.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2FkMpfAU.jpeg&h=fde51fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n霧面design唔燈幾低調, 燈左好炫彩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手感幾好, romer-g感覺幾似茶軸, 但連按同反應快好多<br />\n官網上寫romer-g鍵可以點擊7000萬次, 觸發距離1.5mm, 有26鍵按鍵無衝突設計畀電競選手<br />\n(不過小弟都係wsad+1234玩家, 應該無乜機會用上)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/12/1CGvgq.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2F1CGvgq.jpeg&h=26869c12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/12/CVAHB6.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2FCVAHB6.jpeg&h=02099d93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/12/9kfKVW.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2F9kfKVW.jpeg&h=ea12991f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/12/t0ZhqQ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2Ft0ZhqQ.jpeg&h=22d46517&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/12/bKfa5O.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2FbKfa5O.jpeg&h=78a4aad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n80g, 偏輕, 外型就係一個滑鼠囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一手掌握, 舒服, 用左幾個鐘手腕唔會痛<br />\n最多8個自訂按鈕, 不過都係果句: 應該無乜機會用上<br />\n反應係比普通無鼠快, 詳細靈敏度都係LGS入面調<br />\n整體感覺比較通用, 未必打機先岩<br />\n<br />\nkeyboard cp值: 8.5/10 <br />\nmouse cp值: 9/10<br />\n**有幾耐用睇我幾時出po換新既就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4397f2dba7031ca5ec31d99d385968f2dbf7c4","tid":916942,"uid":334,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T05:21:33.000Z","msg":"香港水魚價，狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1d2da1d8e674a80898ead4b13ac31bf8426cad","tid":916942,"uid":171760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:44:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82cfd06c0049a92b62d13fad610a2faf548b6c0f","tid":916942,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:32:13.000Z","msg":"Rich<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e54ce4e6af94b5b318b5fea1c7c509a9e84f11","tid":916942,"uid":141630,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T08:26:21.000Z","msg":"成兩千蚊一set嘢夠膽寫cp 9/10⋯⋯<img s